snippet: The office of the Paris prosecutor said Chakib Akrouh, who blew himself up in a police raid Nov. 18, was the third jihadist involved in the terror attacks in Paris and its suburbs in November.
abstract: Paris prosecutor says third gunman in Paris terrorist attacks was Belgian-Morrocan man Chakib Akrouh, who killed himself during police raid days after attack.
lead_paragraph: The office of the Paris prosecutor said Chakib Akrouh, who blew himself up in a police raid Nov. 18, was the third jihadist involved in the terror attacks in Paris and its suburbs in November.

headline.main: Third Gunman in Attacks in Paris Area Is Identified
headline.print_headline: Third Gunman in Attacks in Paris Area Is Identified
